description: Cluster designed for tagging OSINT artifacts with relevant OSINT source information. Open-source intelligence (OSINT) is data collected from publicly available sources to be used in an intelligence context. In the intelligence community, the term open refers to overt, publicly available sources (as opposed to covert or clandestine sources). It is not related to open-source software or collective intelligence.
name: OSRS OSINT Source
